data.description: Flushing Schools ~ Move in condition 2 bedroom ranch home situated on a nice sized lot backing up to woods. Stepping into this home you will appreciate the spacious family room with a door-wall leading to the back yard and the cement patio. The Kitchen offers updated white cabinets, newer countertops & tile backsplash, black appliances, and has a breakfast nook. The living room has a large picture window looking out to the front yard and nice hardwood floors. Both bedrooms have hardwood floors have windows looking out to the back yard. The bathroom is remodeled and offers a large tile walk in shower. Main floor laundry room with washer and dryer included. 2 car detached garage with additional storage.
